<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CISIA Spot Alerts - CENT@HOME/CASA</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="badge">üöÄ Free Forever</div>
                <h1>üö® CISIA Spot Alerts</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Never miss a CENT@HOME or CENT@CASA spot opening again</p>
                <p class="hero-description">Get instant Telegram notifications when test spots become available on the official <a href="https://testcisia.it/calendario.php?tolc=cents&lingua=inglese" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CISIA calendar</a>. Automated checks every 30 seconds.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card signup-card">
                <h2>üìù Sign Up for Alerts</h2>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <span class="step-number">1</span>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <strong>Get Your Chat ID</strong>
                            <p>Open Telegram and search for <code>@Cent_alerting_bot</code></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <span class="step-number">2</span>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <strong>Start the Bot</strong>
                            <p>Send <code>/start</code> to the bot - it will reply with your Chat ID</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <span class="step-number">3</span>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <strong>Register Below</strong>
                            <p>Copy your Chat ID (e.g., <code>123456789</code>) and paste it here</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <form action="/signup" method="POST">
                    <label for="chatId">Your Telegram Chat ID</label>
                    <input type="number" 
                           id="chatId" 
                           name="chatId" 
                           required 
                           min="100000000" 
                           max="9999999999" 
                           placeholder="123456789"
                           step="1"
                           autocomplete="off"
                           aria-label="Enter your Telegram Chat ID">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">
                        <span>‚úÖ Start Receiving Alerts</span>
                    </button>
                </form>
                
                <% if (message) { %>
                    <div class="message" role="alert"><%= message %></div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="card info-card">
                    <h3>‚ö° How It Works</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Automated monitoring of CISIA test availability 24/7</li>
                        <li>Instant Telegram alerts when spots open</li>
                        <li>Check the official bot at <a href="https://t.me/Cent_alerting_bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@Cent_alerting_bot</a></li>
                        <li>No spam - only alerts when spots actually become available</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card status-card">
                    <h3>üü¢ System Status</h3>
                    <div class="status-grid">
                        <div class="status-item">
                            <span class="status-label">Bot Status</span>
                            <span class="status-value active">‚óè Live</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-item">
                            <span class="status-label">Check Interval</span>
                            <span class="status-value">30 seconds</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-item">
                            <span class="status-label">Availability</span>
                            <span class="status-value">24/7</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-item">
                            <span class="status-label">Cost</span>
                            <span class="status-value">Free Forever</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <footer class="footer">
                <p>Hosted on <a href="https://render.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Render</a> ‚Ä¢ Open Source on <a href="https://github.com/navdeepg053-cpu/Cisia_alerts_bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></p>
                <p class="footer-note">This is an independent service and is not affiliated with CISIA</p>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
